# Haria Investments — Project Basics

## Stack

- **Next.js 16** (App Router) — read `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` before writing Next.js code; APIs differ from older versions
- **React 19**, **TypeScript 5**, **Tailwind CSS v4**
- Fonts: Geist Sans / Geist Mono via `next/font/google`

## Principles

- Minimize scope — smallest correct diff; no drive-by refactors
- Match existing patterns before introducing new abstractions
- Prefer server components; add `"use client"` only when interactivity or browser APIs require it
- Static assets live in `public/` (e.g. brand video, images)

## File Layout

```
app/           # routes, layouts, global styles
  layout.tsx   # root layout + metadata
  page.tsx     # route pages
  globals.css  # Tailwind import + design tokens
public/        # static files
```

## Commands

- `npm run dev` — local dev
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npm run lint` — ESLint

## Do Not

- Commit secrets (`.env`, API keys)
- Use Pages Router patterns (`getServerSideProps`, `_app.tsx`)
- Guess Next.js 16 APIs — verify in local docs first
